This is called each time any event is processed from the queue when server_urls is empty, correct?

No, every time a metrics event is reported - https://github.com/elastic/apm-agent-java/pull/1295/files#diff-517f2e7d31c3425c5ec7719efd32a06dR151.
The purpose is to continue collecting metrics in the right intervals, because the server_urls is a dynamic config.

Note it doesn't reset the counters and timers as that's only done during serialization.

